  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0d87\u0db3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba - \u0dbb\u0da7\u0da7\u0db8 \u0dc4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Curfew for the West - State of Emergency for the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe has instructed to impose a curfew in the Western Province and to impose a state of emergency in the entire country. This order shall come into force with immediate effect.",
        "The Prime Minister has also ordered the arrest of people who behave violently."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
            "text": "Ranil Wickramasinghe",
            "label": "PERSON"
          },
          {
